summary: Makes Faralda less.. unpleasant.. when trying to enter the College of Winterhold.
descriptionHtml:
Faralda: Cross the bridge at your own peril! The way is dangerous, and the gate will not open! You shall not gain entry! 
Player: May I enter the College? 
Faralda: Oh yeah sure, come on in. 

...what? 

This is a simple mod I made for myself that rearranges some of Faralda\'s dialogue to make her less.. unpleasant.. when trying to enter the College of Winterhold, so I thought I\'d share it. It\'s fully voiced with subtitles. Enjoy.
author: Leazer425
